metadata.description:
{\\rtf1\\ansi\\deff0{\\fonttbl{\\f0 \\fswiss Helvetica;}}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 \\b ResolveLink Callback\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 A polling script that monitors the ResolveLink server for pending REAPER import jobs. When a job arrives, it automatically creates a REAPER project with audio clips from DaVinci Resolve.\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 \\b Requirements:\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 - ResolveLink server running at http://127.0.0.1:3030\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 - curl available in PATH\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 \\b Usage:\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 Run from Actions > Show action list > Load, or assign to a toolbar button. Press the button again to stop polling.\\par}
}

{\\rtf1\\ansi\\deff0{\\fonttbl{\\f0 \\fswiss Helvetica;}}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 \\b ResolveLink Send to Resolve\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 Renders the current REAPER project to WAV, then imports the rendered audio into DaVinci Resolve via the ResolveLink server. Creates a new audio track in the active timeline.\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 \\b Requirements:\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 - ResolveLink server running at http://127.0.0.1:3030\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 - DaVinci Resolve open with a timeline\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 - curl available in PATH\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 \\b Usage:\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 Assign to a toolbar button. Click to render and send audio to DaVinci Resolve.\\par}
}

{\\rtf1\\ansi\\deff0{\\fonttbl{\\f0 \\fswiss Helvetica;}}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 \\b ResolveLink Update Project\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 Syncs REAPER items to match the current DaVinci Resolve timeline. When video cuts change in DaVinci, press this to update REAPER item positions and durations. Your REAPER effects, volume, and pan settings are preserved.\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 \\b Requirements:\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 - ResolveLink server running at http://127.0.0.1:3030\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 - DaVinci Resolve open with a timeline\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 - curl available in PATH\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 \\b Usage:\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 Workspace > Scripts > ResolveLink > Update Project\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 Or assign to a toolbar button.\\par}
}

{\\rtf1\\ansi\\deff0{\\fonttbl{\\f0 \\fswiss Helvetica;}}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 \\b ResolveLink Panel\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 Unified control panel combining all ResolveLink functions into one UI:\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 - Toggle Callback (on/off)\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 - Send to Resolve (render + import)\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 - Update Project (sync to DaVinci timeline)\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 - Live status and log\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 \\b Requirements:\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 - ResolveLink server running at http://127.0.0.1:3030\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 - curl available in PATH\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 \\b Usage:\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 Actions > Show action list > Load > select this file\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 Or assign to a toolbar button.\\par}
}

{\\rtf1\\ansi\\deff0{\\fonttbl{\\f0 \\fswiss Helvetica;}}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 \\b \\fs36 ResolveLink\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 Bridge between DaVinci Resolve, After Effects, and REAPER.\\par}
{\\pard \\ql \\f0 \\sa180 \\li0 \\fi0 This repository contains REAPER scripts for the ResolveLink workflow.\\par}
}
